Bourgas is the fourth-largest city in Bulgaria after: ; Sofia, Plovdiv, Varna ; Sofia, Varna, Russe ; Sofia, Russe, Plovdiv; Sofia, Plovdiv, Silistra
The name of the city is derived from the Latin word "burgos" which meaning: ; "tower" ; "city" ; "largest" ; "captane"
